  Fix (inside validate() after detecting an error):
```js
if (!result.valid) {
  srUtils.markInvalid(field, errorEl);               // existing
  field.setAttribute('aria-invalid', 'true');        // ← add this line
} else {
  field.removeAttribute('aria-invalid');             // ← add this line (in the valid branch)
}
```

